## Design Overview

Countrast presents a clean, data-focused design system optimized for comparing country statistics. The design emphasizes clarity and readability with a minimal color palette dominated by warm stone tones and neutral grays. The typography system uses a monospace font (Reddit Mono) for data and a sans-serif font (Rubik) for UI elements, creating a clear visual hierarchy between data and interface elements. The layout is grid-based with responsive breakpoints, allowing the comparison interface to adapt seamlessly from mobile to desktop. Interactive elements use subtle transitions and hover states to provide clear feedback without distracting from the data visualization.

